1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 13, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104nuj1665702834673.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nuj1665702834673.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nuj1665702834673.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"nuj1665702834673\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                           \n Modality &amp; Attachment\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify the modality of a form, and whether it is attached or detached to its parent.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nuj1665702834673__p_d9566e1_d9567e1_d9568e1\">For non-modal forms, you can override the detached definition at run time by using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/attached</span> in the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">newinstance</span> statement. This switch is ignored if the form is activated as a modal form.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"nuj1665702834673__table_d1004e1_d1005e1_d1006e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nuj1665702834673__table_d1004e1_d1005e1_d1006e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nuj1665702834673__table_d1004e1_d1005e1_d1006e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nuj1665702834673__table_d1004e1_d1005e1_d1006e1__entry__1\">\n Modal, Attached\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nuj1665702834673__table_d1004e1_d1005e1_d1006e1__entry__2\">\n Modal forms are always attached and have the following behavior:\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nuj1665702834673__li_d4415e1_d4416e1_d4417e1\">A new instance of the component is a child of the form that created it.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nuj1665702834673__li_d4418e1_d4419e1_d4420e1\">When the parent of this component instance closes, this instance, and all of its children are also closed.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nuj1665702834673__li_d4421e1_d4422e1_d4423e1\">When the parent of this component instance is iconized, this instance and all of its children are also iconized.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nuj1665702834673__table_d1004e1_d1005e1_d1006e1__entry__1\">\n Non-Modal, Attached\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nuj1665702834673__table_d1004e1_d1005e1_d1006e1__entry__2\">\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nuj1665702834673__li_d4424e1_d4425e1_d4426e1\">A new instance is a child of the component instance that created it.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nuj1665702834673__li_d4427e1_d4428e1_d4429e1\">When the parent of this instance closes, this instance, and all of its children are also closed.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nuj1665702834673__table_d1004e1_d1005e1_d1006e1__entry__1\">\n Non-Modal, Detached\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nuj1665702834673__table_d1004e1_d1005e1_d1006e1__entry__2\">\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nuj1665702834673__li_d4430e1_d4431e1_d4432e1\">Each new, detached instance remains active until it closes itself or until the application closes.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nuj1665702834673__li_d4433e1_d4434e1_d4435e1\">You can override this definition in ProcScript at run time by specifying <code class=\"ph codeph\">MODALITY=MODAL</code> with the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">newinstance</span> ProcScript statement.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530431\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530431\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Modality & Attachment Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 13, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Modality & Attachment Specify the modality of a form, and whether it is attached or detached to its parent. For non-modal forms, you can override the detached definition at run time by using /attached in the newinstance statement. This switch is ignored if the form is activated as a modal form. Table 1. Values Value Meaning Modal, Attached Modal forms are always attached and have the following behavior: A new instance of the component is a child of the form that created it. When the parent of this component instance closes, this instance, and all of its children are also closed. When the parent of this component instance is iconized, this instance and all of its children are also iconized. Non-Modal, Attached A new instance is a child of the component instance that created it. When the parent of this instance closes, this instance, and all of its children are also closed. Non-Modal, Detached Each new, detached instance remains active until it closes itself or until the application closes. You can override this definition in ProcScript at run time by specifying MODALITY=MODAL with the newinstance ProcScript statement. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}